'''Winda Warrick''' was the youngest member of the [[Warrick family/Legends|Warrick family]].
She was [[Weechee Warrick|Weechee]], [[Widdle Warrick/Legends|Willy]], and [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket's]] precious baby sister, and her mother, [[Shodu Warrick|Shodu]], spent most of her time taking care of her during Wicket's adolescence. [[Deej Warrick]] was her father.

